bjf 

This is small utility to display all neccessary informations of the file in one place.

Utility shows in file section:

1) filename
2) full path
3) size in bytes
4) block size
5) number of allocated blocks
6) inode number
7) number of hard links
8) device id
9) time of last access
10) time of last modification
11) time of last change
12) permissions

and in user section:

13) UID and GID of the owner
14) name of the owner and name of the group
15) gecos field
16) home folder path
17) user shell


